    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just about 'what people think' though. it's who i am. i spent twenty years building that version of myself. now that person is gone. there's nothing left underneath to 'find' or 'rebuild'. it feels like a hollow shell. how are you supposed to exist when the person you were literally doesn't exist anymore?",
