      "content": "\"letting it settle in\"... i dont know. it just feels permanent. like i'm just waiting for the rest of my life to catch up to the fact that i'm already finished. everything i once cared about is just a ghost now. is there actually any point to trying to find a \"new reality\" when the old one was the only one that mattered? everything feels so empty.",
